rest_of_day_open: I think it will go well. I am excited to get my new kitten next week so I will have that to look forward to for the next few days. Also, I have enough food and I just cashed out my prolific account so I have some cash. I took care of most everything.
critical_positive: We both had things to talk about with each other, we were able to keep the conversation going. critical_negative: There were some brief silences that were just a tiny bit awkward but that was just because those generally are. I feel like I was the first to speak when that happened most of the time, but that was ok. I also thought my partner was a bit boring, not too interesting.

critical_positive: We seemed to have similar thoughts on several key issues. This allowed us to make more assumptions than you normally would with a stranger, which opens up a larger avenue for conversation. critical_negative: There weren't technical "issues," however ANY telecom between Texas and New Hampshire will have a delay. Especially when video is involved.
